===Noun===
'''gown''' ([[gowns]])

#A loose, flowing upper [[garment]]
#The ordinary outer dress of a woman; as, a [[calico]] or silk gown.
#The official [[robe]] of certain professional men and [[scholar]]s, as university students and officers, [[barrister]]s, [[judge]]s, etc.; hence, the dress of peace; the dress of civil officers, in distinction from military.
#A loose [[wrapper]] worn by gentlemen within doors; a [[dressing gown]].
#Any sort of dress or [[garb]].